<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1">
		
		<title><%= @experiment.title .html_safe %></title>

		<!-- Loading third party fonts -->
		<link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
		

	<style type="text/css">
		@media only screen and (max-width : 640px) {

        .container {
            margin-top: 0px;
           }
 
	</style>

	</head>


	<body>
		
		<div class="site-content">

		

			<main class="main-content">
				<div class="page-head">
					<div class="container">
						
						<h1 class="page-title"><%= @experiment.title .html_safe %></h1>
					</div>
				</div>
                





                <div class="fullwidth-block">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae.</p>
							
							<p>Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas aspernatur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur.</p>

							
							
						</div>
						  <div class="col-sm-6">
			
							<iframe  class="macbook" src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/<%= @experiment.youtube_link .html_safe %>?rel=0&autoplay=<%= params[:autoplay] || 0 %>' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen></iframe>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>










				<div class="fullwidth-block">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<h2>Theory</h2>
							<p><%= @experiment.description .html_safe %></p>
							<p><%= @experiment.lab.title %></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<h2>components used</h2>
							<p><%= @experiment.components %></p>
                 			<a><%= link_to "Back", root_path, class: "button" %></a>
							<% if user_signed_in? %>
                            <% if @experiment.user_id == current_user.id %>
                            <%= link_to "Edit", edit_experiment_path(@experiment) %>
                            <%= link_to "Delete", experiment_path(@experiment), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure?" } %>
                            <% end %>
                           <% end %>

						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			 <div id="disqus_thread"></div>
